Symbol.Script_3D:
!-----------3d--------------------- if show_el < EPS then end IF gs_detlevel_3D_m < EPS THEN END CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL one_ConID=0 returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, sMat, gs_InsMat, MEP_cline_pen, show_el
! Horiz. Disch. Sewage Pump
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- SEWAGE PUMP --- !
unID = 1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT B/2, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, -B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, 0, ZZYZX, unID: unID=unID+1
footH = ConPosZ_1-bottomThk/2 footTck = 0.05 * B
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ! Detailed
RESOL 16
GROUP "pumpBody" ADDz ConPosZ_1 ROTy -90 REVOLVE 3,360,1+2+16+32, -bottomThk/2, (B-bottomThk)/2, 1, 0,1, 801, bottomThk/2, (B-bottomThk)/2, 1001 DEL 2 ENDGROUP PLACEGROUP "pumpBody"
ADDz ConPosZ_1 ROTy -90 REVOLVE 4,360,1+2+16+32, bottomThk/2, motorLowerD/2, 2, bottomThk/2+motorMiddleZ, motorLowerD/2, 2, bottomThk/2+2*motorMiddleZ, motorUpperD/2, 2, ZZYZX-ConPosZ_1, motorUpperD/2, 2 DEL 2
GROUP "connection" ADD ConPosX_1, 0, ConPosZ_1 !! REVOLVE 5,360, 16+32, !! -ConLength_1, ConWidth_1/2, 2, !! -ConLength_1, 1.6*ConWidth_1/2, 2, !! -ConLength_1+0.004, 1.6*ConWidth_1/2, 2, !! -ConLength_1+0.004, ConWidth_1/2, 2, !! ABS(ConPosX_1)-(B-bottomThk)/2, ConWidth_1/2, 2
REVOLVE 2,360, 16+32, 0, ConWidth_1/2, 2, ABS(ConPosX_1)-(B-bottomThk)/2, ConWidth_1/2, 2
DEL 1
ENDGROUP
PLACEGROUP SUBGROUP ("connection", "pumpBody")
KILLGROUP "connection" KILLGROUP "pumpBody"
IF footH > 0.001 THEN TOLER 0.05
ROTy -90 FOR i=1 TO 3 ADDz (B-bottomThk)/2 - footTck REVOLVE 3,360, 1+2+16+32, footH, footTck, 1, 0.1 * footH, 0.5*footTck, 1, 0, 0.001, 1001 DEL 1 ROTx 120 NEXT i DEL 4 ENDIF ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN ! Simple
GROUP "pumpBody2" ADDz ConPosZ_1 ROTy -90 REVOLVE 3,360,1+2+16+32, -bottomThk/2, (B-bottomThk)/2, 1, 0,1, 801, bottomThk/2, (B-bottomThk)/2, 1001 DEL 2 ENDGROUP PLACEGROUP "pumpBody2"
ADDz ConPosZ_1 ROTy -90 REVOLVE 2,360,1+2+16+32, bottomThk/2, motorLowerD/2, 2, ZZYZX-ConPosZ_1, motorUpperD/2, 2 DEL 2
GROUP "connection2" ADD ConPosX_1, 0, ConPosZ_1 !! REVOLVE 3,360, 16+32, !! -ConLength_1, 1.6*ConWidth_1/2, 2, !! -ConLength_1, ConWidth_1/2, 2, !! ABS(ConPosX_1)-(B-bottomThk)/2, ConWidth_1/2, 2
REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+16+32, 0, ConWidth_1/2, 2, ABS(ConPosX_1)-(B-bottomThk)/2, ConWidth_1/2, 1
DEL 1 ENDGROUP
PLACEGROUP SUBGROUP ("connection2", "pumpBody2")
KILLGROUP "connection2" KILLGROUP "pumpBody2"
IF footH > 0 THEN TOLER 0.2
ROTy -90 FOR i=1 TO 3 ADDz (B-bottomThk)/2 - footTck REVOLVE 2,360, 1+2+16+32, footH, footTck, 1, 0 * footH, 0.5*footTck, 1 DEL 1 ROTx 120 NEXT i DEL 4 ENDIF ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
DEL TOP RESOL res
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_1 = 0, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData
END
Symbol.Script_2D:
!-----------2d--------------------- if show_el < EPS then end IF gs_detlevel_2D_m < EPS THEN END CALL "MEP_m_RequestSystemGlobals" PARAMETERS ALL one_ConID=0 returned_parameters gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, MEP_cline_type, MEP_cline_pen, show_el
! Horiz. Disch. Sewage Pump
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
unID = 1 DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 THEN ! Top
! --- SEWAGE PUMP --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 B/2, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1
IF GLOB_CONTEXT <> 22 THEN POLY2_B 2, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0, 901, B/2, 360, 4001
CIRCLE2 0,0, motorLowerD/2 CIRCLE2 0,0, motorUpperD/2
dx = SQR((B/2)^2 - (ConWidth_1/2)^2)
! POLY2_B 8, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, ! ConPosX_1-ConLength_1, 1.6*ConWidth_1/2, 1, ! ConPosX_1-ConLength_1+0.004, 1.6*ConWidth_1/2, 1, ! ConPosX_1-ConLength_1+0.004, ConWidth_1/2, 1, ! -dx, ConWidth_1/2, 1, ! -dx, -ConWidth_1/2, 1, ! ConPosX_1-ConLength_1+0.004, -ConWidth_1/2, 1, ! ConPosX_1-ConLength_1+0.004, -1.6*ConWidth_1/2, 1, ! ConPosX_1-ConLength_1, -1.6*ConWidth_1/2, 1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1, ConWidth_1/2, 1, -dx, ConWidth_1/2, 1, -dx, -ConWidth_1/2, 1, ConPosX_1, -ConWidth_1/2, 0
! LINE2 ConPosX_1-ConLength_1+0.004, ConWidth_1/2, ! ConPosX_1-ConLength_1+0.004, -ConWidth_1/2 ENDIF ENDIF DEL TOP
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 (SYMB_MIRRORED - NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED)) * (DrawingNum > 1) * SYMB_ROTANGLE
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * SYMB_MIRRORED, 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1, ConEdgeVisible_1 = 0, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData
DEL 1
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
!-----------Основной--------------------- success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "show_axis", show_axis) success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "show_axis_and", show_axis_and) success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "show_isol", show_isol) success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "show_conventions", show_conventions) success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "show_size", show_size) success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "gs_detlevel_2D_m",gs_detlevel_2D_m) success = LIBRARYGLOBAL ("Libraryflobals-mep", "gs_detlevel_3D_m", gs_detlevel_3D_m) call "Показ_систем" PARAMETERS All isMep=1 RETURNED_PARAMETERS show_el, syst_name
! Horiz. Disch. Sewage Pump
EPS = 0.0001
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
minD = MIN(2*ConWidth_1, ABS(ConPosX_1)) IF B<minD THEN B=minD ENDIF
ConWidth_1 = MIN(ConWidth_1, B/2)
bottomThk = 1.2 * ConWidth_1
motorLowerD = B-bottomThk motorUpperD = 0.8 * motorLowerD motorMiddleZ = 0.15 * ZZYZX
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z
Symbol.Script_UI:
! Horiz. Disch. Sewage Pump
UI_DIALOG `Специальные Параметры MEP`
DIM ui_vis_attr[4][4] FOR i = 1 TO 4 FOR j = 1 TO 4 ui_vis_attr[i][j] = 0 NEXT j NEXT i ui_vis_attr[1][1] = 2 ui_vis_attr[1][2] = 1 ui_vis_attr[1][3] = 7
ui_vis_attr[2][1] = 1 ui_vis_attr[2][2] = 237 ui_vis_attr[2][3] = 68 ui_vis_attr[2][4] = 14
DIM ui_con_type[1] ui_con_type[1] = 0
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS ALL ui_vis_attr = ui_vis_attr, ui_centerline_vars = 0, ui_con_type = ui_con_type, ui_system_var_pos = 2, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
Symbol.Script_VL:
! Horiz. Disch. Sewage Pump
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
! --- MAIN PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN minD = MIN(2*ConWidth_1, ABS(ConPosX_1)) IF B<minD THEN B=minD PARAMETERS B=minD ENDIF VALUES "B" RANGE [minD, ]
minW = B IF A<minW THEN A=minW PARAMETERS A=minW ENDIF VALUES "A" RANGE [minW,]
minH = ConPosZ_1+ConWidth_1 IF ZZYZX<minH THEN ZZYZX=minH PARAMETERS ZZYZX=minH ENDIF VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [minH,] ENDIF LOCK "A"
! --- OBJECT SPECIFIC PARAMETERS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN maxPX = -B/2 ConPosX_1=maxPX PARAMETERS ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1
minPZ = 0.6*ConWidth_1 maxPZ = ZZYZX/2 VALUES "ConPosZ_1" RANGE[minPZ, maxPZ] IF ConPosZ_1<minPZ THEN ConPosZ_1=minPZ PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1=minPZ ENDIF IF ConPosZ_1>maxPZ THEN ConPosZ_1=maxPZ PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1=maxPZ ENDIF IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" THEN ConPosX_1 = -A/2 PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = -A/2 ELSE PARAMETERS A = ABS(ConPosX_1) + B/2 ENDIF ENDIF
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 1
! --- SEWAGE CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Подключение Трубы Канализации`
ConDVecX = -1 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = 1 ConWVecZ = 0
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN maxCW = B/2
VALUES "ConLength_1" RANGE [0,] VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, maxCW] VALUES "ConDepth_1" RANGE (0, maxCW]
IF ConWidth_1<0 THEN ConWidth_1=EPS PARAMETERS ConWidth_1=EPS ENDIF IF ConWidth_1>maxCW THEN ConWidth_1=maxCW PARAMETERS ConWidth_1=maxCW ENDIF
VALUES "ConWallThickness_1" RANGE [0, ConWidth_1/2] ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
